casebody.data:
Lorine SPENCE
v.
Laura WASCO. No. 359P15. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Oct. 27, 2015. Lorine Spence, for Spence, Lorine.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Plaintiff on the 26th of October 2015 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 27th of October 2015."
